<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1080205"><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>这是基于《钢之守护神》制作的同人扩展规则，仅供学习与交流，勿作商业用途</strong></span></span><br><br><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>神兵级/Gigantes&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">■类别解说&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br>神兵级是带有强人工智能的守护神类别，设计上不止能辅助连结者驾驶，更拥有独立作战能力。&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>神兵级的连结者必须穿戴「铁驭机甲」(英文：Dominator)。这种机甲以Altima制作，而且带有一定立体机动作战能力，与守护神无异。 在连结者进入成神兵级的驾驶舱时，连结者将会透过铁驭机甲上的NLS功能与神兵级成为一体，发挥出匹敌一支部队的性能。&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>※NLS：神经介面连接&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>智能核心遵从三项最重要的协议：&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>协议一：与连结者连线。&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>协议二：坚守任务。&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br>协议三：保护连结者。&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br><br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">所有数据、特技规则、特技、物品已完补</span></strong><br>我直接上传个zip档上来比较容易明白<br>里面全都是html档，直接拉到浏览器就能看到<br><br><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">28/12/2020 神兵级砍掉重练决定</span></span><br><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">14/01/2021 神兵级新生版本发布(核心玩法更变注意，筑构简易化、特技表约5成砍掉重练)</span></span><br><br>网盘连结(暂停)<br><br>如果想直接看网上版可以看谷狗连结<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1KovuRbDq1cOLP8HPSqhz5EJqAYoTHqEwVZkX7o5wMKY/edit?usp=sharing</div></div></div><br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">类别介绍</span></strong><br>这边我以官方仍未动土的塔拉布鲁自治洲上开刀了。不过这只是为到方便而写的背景设定，GM们自行决定要不要采用。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTa